title: How to Make Peach Cake

steps.headline: Spread the peaches in baking pan.
Mix the remaining ingredients, except brown sugar and milk, together in mixing bowl; spread over the top of the peaches.
Bake until a toothpick inserted into cake comes out clean, about 30-35 minutes.
Make the topping.
steps.description: Combine brown sugar and milk in small bowl.

steps.headline: Drizzle the sugar mixture on top of cake and return the cake to the oven, and bake another 2-3 minutes.

text: Preheat oven to 350ºF. Lightly grease the baking pan. Spread the peaches in baking pan.  Mix the remaining ingredients, except brown sugar and milk, together in mixing bowl; spread over the top of the peaches.  Bake until a toothpick inserted into cake comes out clean, about 30-35 minutes.  Make the topping. Combine brown sugar and milk in small bowl. Drizzle the sugar mixture on top of cake and return the cake to the oven, and bake another 2-3 minutes.  Cut into eight pieces.  Finished.
